	<description>	
		Ghostbutter is a label for weird, spooky-cute &amp; fun games, founded by siblings Konstantin &amp; Elenor Kopka.
	</description>
		
	<histories>
		<history>
			<header>Early history</header>
			<text>Founded in 2015 by sibling duo Konstantin &amp; Elenor Kopka, Ghostbutter as a studio is still very much in development. So far, they have made a couple of tiny games, such as "A Good Cup of Tea", "Ghost Coin" &amp; "Dress Code: Human". Ghostbutter's biggest project so far, "Wunderdoktor", will be released on October 11th, 2017.</text>
		</history>
